_json.gridTitle: How much I paid for a garden renovation
_json.description: How much I paid for a garden renovation - YouTube - Over the past year, I've been giving the backyard of my new home a garden makeover. It started as a square of grass with a lovely glass greenhouse in the corner. Bit by bit, I've added a rose arbor, raised beds, a patio raised bed, and pea gravel garden paths.
